original_title: NJPW Road To Tokyo Dome - Day 6
overview: In the last event leading into Wrestle Kingdom 8 at the Tokyo Dome, NJPW returns to Korakuen Hall to see 2013 off with a bang. Matches include Kazuchika Okada & Shinsuke Nakamura vs. Hiroshi Tanahashi & Tetsuya Naito, Minoru Suzuki vs. YOSHI-HASHI and Kota Ibushi & Togi Makabe vs. CHAOS (Tomohiro Ishii & Yujiro Takahashi)
title: NJPW Road To Tokyo Dome - Day 6
